            <description><![CDATA[【你可能每天在无效刷牙<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】中华预防医学会指出：“我国有超过半数的人都达不到有效刷牙”。半数国人每天假装刷牙！赶集式刷牙、伐木式刷牙、闭嘴自由发挥式刷牙……不好好刷牙会给牙菌斑留机会，蛀牙、牙周炎、牙石都跟它有关。你每天有在好好刷牙吗？世界公认最标准的巴氏（BASS)刷牙法，宝子们再来复习一遍👇🏻（via 健康界）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4749391312126090" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">健康界的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/9e0564d7ly1h0h96c93e2j20nq0dcmxk.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/9710IqRIlx07UE9cG7rW0104120068AQ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=854x480.28.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688678080&amp;ssig=yCr0JR3yMS&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/td4R5Zdclx07UE9cTUtG010412003WsI0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688678080&amp;ssig=MNNoTzsrg%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4749391312126090&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
