            <description><![CDATA[【手腕上鼓个泡，到底该不该捏爆？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】手上长了个“大肿包”，不痒也不红，可以捏爆吗？打住！你这不是蚊子包，是腱鞘囊肿 ！不小心把囊肿按破了，也多半不会出大问题。因为在手外科门诊，对于小的腱鞘囊肿，医生们也这么干。但，你自己捏，和医生捏，区别很大👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfmx3ig0v7j20u058owsu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfmx3ivplsj20u01yxwim.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfn5z7ocm7j20u04vxnaz.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfn5z6rdzkj20u02ftdl9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
