            <description><![CDATA[【注意！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%BE%AE%E7%AC%91%E5%9E%8B%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E5%AF%9F%E8%A7%89%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%BE%AE%E7%AC%91%E5%9E%8B%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E5%AF%9F%E8%A7%89%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#微笑型抑郁症不易被察觉#</span></a>】抑郁症不等同于“坏心情”，而是一种疾病。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%894%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%81%E5%85%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%894%E4%B8%AA%E5%BE%81%E5%85%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#抑郁症早期有4个征兆#</span></a>：①总高兴不起来；②失去兴趣；③认知功能损害；④没有明确原因的长期失眠等。此外，还有<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%232%E7%A7%8D%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E5%AF%9F%E8%A7%89%23&amp;extparam=%232%E7%A7%8D%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E5%AF%9F%E8%A7%89%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#2种抑郁症不易被察觉#</span></a>：微笑型抑郁和隐匿性抑郁。👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4616006363185155" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1200.667/0033ImPzly1gonq4r2ip8j60xc0iq7wh02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/Tw7UAoculx07Lb4ajrRC01041200Q5h20E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;trans_finger=1f0da16358befad33323e3a1b7f95fc9&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688678037&amp;ssig=yiYpXd2up2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/9j5PCMbzlx07Lb49UeGc01041200oLmh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;trans_finger=62b30a3f061b162e421008955c73f536&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688678037&amp;ssig=nrVnnDcUc4&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/w33eNgrBlx07Lb49LULS01041200fTbN0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;trans_finger=40a32e8439c5409a63ccf853562a60ef&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688678037&amp;ssig=9jeKAX%2F8xT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4616006363185155&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
